data.description: Welcome to this Charming 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home Nestled in a Desirable Cross Creek Neighborhood, Boasting 1655 sq. ft. of Comfortable Living Space.  This Modern Home Offers an Inviting Open Layout, Perfect for Entertaining Guests. The Well-Designed Floor Plan Features Split Bedrooms, Ensuring Privacy and Tranquility. The Spacious Kitchen is a Chef's Delight, with ample Cabinets and Counter space, Ideal for Culinary Creations and Gatherings. The Primary Bathroom is a Luxurious Retreat, featuring a Tiled Shower and Double Vanities, Providing both Style and Functionality. Additionally, this Eco-Friendly Home Includes SOLAR PANELS, offering Energy Efficiency and Cost Savings. Don't miss the opportunity to Make this House your Home Sweet Home!
